{
  "texts": [
    "This acknowledgment of AI's boundaries enables educators to refine their preparation strategies more meticulously, promising a more effective integration of AI technologies.",
    "While recent studies have illuminated the varied efficacy of ChatGPT under different circumstances, it is essential to acknowledge the ongoing advancements in AI technology.",
    "Despite all the concerns, ChatGPT remains one of the most user-friendly, and accessible LLMs available for educational use and research.",
    "Its ability to generate human-like content makes it a valuable tool for exploring the intersection of AI and chemistry education.",
    "Given these concerns surrounding ChatGPT's application in educational contexts, there emerges a compelling need for a thorough evaluation of LLMs within chemistry education."
  ]
}